<br>
Ones i can know of ATM:<br>
<br>
Loraks in POS (Those frogs in the forest, hurricane, typhoon) - Lvl 60 exactly.<br>
<br>
Crystaline Golems in POV - con yellow to me at 61 but they don't summon or cast.<br>
<br>
<br>
Thats all i know of, just got 60 last weekend so i'm looking for new places to charm with a druid for his snare.  Hopefully beckon will work as well as boltrans did.    Love that charm XP! Got 60 in a day just tagging along with a druid friend in POS, he was going the charming and i was tashing/ hasteing/ slowing/  mez.<br>
<br>
Lets see what we can come up with fellow chanters!<br>
